Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.08,0:00:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你愿意看看我的画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.85,0:02:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个久攻不下的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾吸引无数人前去挑战 却均被击破的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有人愿意欣赏我的画了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 大神哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 桂马 说了多少遍别边打游戏边吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾露 看好桂马别让他被车撞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神哥哥 不好好看路会被车撞的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽今天还是那么有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that they just seem to be cleverer as they obey our command
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木 翻译刚才那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看似聪明到会好好服从我们的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为答对就行了吗 啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处处有人家 坐落如蛛网
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:31.34,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出自荻原朔太郎「遗传」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧 大神哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还愿意称我为大神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此无能的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是自信满满的大神 今天到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\frz18\move(420,380,370,340)\fscx70\fscy70}桂马 今天又在画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如传闻一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久攻不下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是连大神哥哥都无法攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是个相当难的游戏啊
